welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Arnouville-les-Gonesse! Get ready to experience the charm and beauty of our city, known for its quaint streets, delicious cuisine, and rich history. We invite you to explore and discover all that Arnouville-les-Gonesse has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Le Bourget Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Le Bourget Airport, primarily used for private and business flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The oldest and largest terminal at Charles De Gaulle Airport, serving international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: The newest and busiest terminal at Charles De Gaulle Airport, divided into 7 sub-terminals.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Charles De Gaulle Airport, mainly used for low-cost airlines and domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport, but may require reconnection every 15 minutes.

terminals.name: Terminal 1

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Paris Cergy Pontoise Airport, mainly used for domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orly Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Orly Airport, mainly used for low-cost airlines.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but may have limited coverage in some areas.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Private Terminal
